{"tid":2177779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TikTok全球CEO 上任三個月跳船","createTime":"2020-08-28T03:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T03:22:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff32c49cc0a1f905975f8e535c656bcd3150eeb2","tid":2177779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/AOQJCMSJ5NFGLC4SV34QHSRA3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FAOQJCMSJ5NFGLC4SV34QHSRA3M%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONtT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=b750db27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FAOQJCMSJ5NFGLC4SV34QHSRA3M%2F&h=ad02be3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/AOQJCMSJ5NFGLC4SV34QHSRA3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nTikTok全球CEO 上任三個月跳船<br />\n<br />\n■TikTok全球行政總裁梅耶爾<br />\n<br />\n中國短片分享平台抖音海外版TikTok入稟美國法院，反制總統特朗普的封殺令之際，上任僅三個月的TikTok全球行政總裁梅耶爾（Kevin Mayer）宣佈辭職。他表示，近期政治環境突變，公司或需作出調整，決定請辭。美媒CNBC昨引述消息稱，梅耶爾離職顯示，TikTok出售給微軟的交易或可在未來48小時內完成。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美制裁南海造島華企  數十高層禁入境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或因印美封殺令<br />\n<br />\n梅耶爾昨致函全體員工，宣佈辭任。他提到：「近數星期，政治環境突變，公司或需要因此作出一些調整，我的崗位將會受到影響，對此我思考了一番，我决定離開。」TikTok母公司字節跳動表示，尊重梅耶爾决定。據報，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n字節跳動創辦人兼行政總裁張一鳴指，梅耶爾在字節跳動堪稱最具挑戰性時刻加入，指要在一間發展得那麼快的公司領導，本。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/澎湃網"},{"pid":"fd86acd9eb94a6607103f75bc93aaea98ea565f7","tid":2177779,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱過左試用期就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d960af7a14e485c0fde31f0d66aeac05f5dbe2ae","tid":2177779,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f724c9e51e19729f79551216